title: Animalogy Conquest of the Animal World - DILM-Ak0
description:
Animalogy: Conquest of the Animal World

Animalogy: Conquest of the Animal World provides a good source of information pertaining to animal use, animal consumption, animal conservation, and animal protection.

Also included is a vast URL section pertaining to various topics and sub-topics related to the body of the book and more. 

My book is relatively easy to read and you will find the URL section of immense help to you in doing additional research for this subject matter.
